    h2 Labels
    span.c-label 3
    span.c-label Something Important
    hr
    h2 Tags
    span.c-tag Infrastructure
    span.c-tag Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL)
    
    hr
    include _sg-typography

  include includes/_footer